{"tid":599291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴錯公司仲聲大夾惡？奧客食譚仔三哥去錯譚仔 Facebook 洗版","createTime":"2018-03-20T09:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T09:33:53.000Z","uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03b48fbd6d122978c3f26891df5dc6c8f7ff418f","tid":599291,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"劉德華講過「今時今日咁嘅服務態度&hellip;」，如果在商店、餐廳遇到店員不好的服務態度，應該會像 Facebook 用戶「Melo Himeda」很生氣吧！事關&nbsp;Melo Himeda 早前使用電話外賣服務在土瓜灣店的「譚仔三哥」叫外賣，前往到門市時看見有信用卡（Visa）以及八達通機，誰不知卻被店員告知外賣僅限現金付款，而&nbsp;Melo Himeda 則認為為什麼同樣都是付款但僅限於現金，而且聲稱員工編號 2401 的店員（該店店長）態度惡劣，甚至對顧客說粗粗言穢語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來這只是一單普通的投訴事件，但&nbsp;Melo Himeda 毫不知道「譚仔三哥」與「譚仔」屬於不同的公司，竟然在「譚仔」的 Facebook 專業大罵其公司的服務態度非常差。雖然「譚仔」的 Facebook 管理員已經澄清其公司與「譚仔三哥」無關，但仍然無法安撫&nbsp;Melo Himeda 的弱小心靈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/20/jointedheart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2Fjointedheart%2F&d=ZhIX5m104SAY8N8dsYFrA4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=07787ce0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/20/jointedheart/</a>"},{"pid":"a5b8a855f2d0eb6a84c44ed161bb56f92921160a","tid":599291,"uid":89530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫奧客？<br />\n國藉嚟？"},{"pid":"21f20384a4413582682aff8a8b39f03091d13133","tid":599291,"uid":143760,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5b8a855f2d0eb6a84c44ed161bb56f92921160a","tid":599291,"uid":89530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫奧客？<br />\n國藉嚟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"台灣:奧客/漚客<br />\n香港:閪客<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08008f52955d286faf2b17acabcc27a48dcea15e","tid":599291,